#: ../../source/integrate/zoom.rst:8
msgid ""
"Reduce friction and time lost to coordinating meetings and switching "
"between apps by integrating Zoom with Mattermost. Make it easy for your "
"teams to start both spontaneous video calls directly from Mattermost "
"channels."
msgstr ""

